      <title>印度债务将迎来加入指数以来的首次月度流出</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/indian-bonds-set-for-first-monthly-outflow-since-index-inclusion</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于与美国国债的收益率差距缩小，印度主权债券有望自被纳入摩根大通旗舰指数以来首次出现月度资金流出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-29/indian-bonds-set-for-first-monthly-outflow-since-index-inclusion</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 29 Nov 2024 03:14:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
